---
title: Creamy Chicken Sausage & Tortelloni Bake with Zucchini, Crispy Panko & Scallions
description: Think a big bowl of cheesy stuffed pasta can’t get any better? Think again! In this recipe, we toss tender, cheese-stuffed tortelloni with golden-brown sautéed zucchini in a velvety lemon-scallion cream sauce. Shower with panko breadcrumbs that crisp up to an enticing golden brown in the oven, and dig into a deliciously cozy vegetarian dinner idea that’s ready in just 30 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-sausage-tortelloni-bake-c3ceb557.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-chicken-sausage-tortelloni-bake-63c8277a3a6d8bd6aa02bfaa-8b7ae1b7.pdf
